## Wiring

| Arduino Pin | Connects To |
|-------------|-------------|
| A4 (SDA)    | LCD SDA     |
| A5 (SCL)    | LCD SCL     |
| D2          | Button      |
| D10         | HC-05 RX    |
| D11         | HC-05 TX    |
| 5V          | LCD VCC, HC-05 VCC |
| GND         | LCD GND, Button, HC-05 GND |
